(1382, 'Icoface 60 gm sunscreen cream', 'ايكوفيس صنسكرين كريم 60 جم', '', '297', 'Zinc oxide+hyaluronic acid+collagen vitamin c', 'Iconic pharmaceutical', 'Cream', 'كريم', '', 'Sunscreen', '60 gm', 'Zinc can be used for the treatment and prevention of zinc deficiency/its consequences, including stunted growth and acute diarrhea in children, and slowed wound healing. It is also utilized for boosting the immune system, treating the common cold and recurrent ear infections, as well as preventing lower respiratory tract infections [L2172].', '', '', 898, '2022-08-19', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(28422, 'Treczimus 0.03% topical oint. 20 gm', 'تريكزيمس مرهم 0.03% 20 جرام', '78', '114', 'Tacrolimus', 'Marcyrl co.', 'Oint', 'مرهم', 'علاج حالات الصدفية.', 'Immunosuppressants.psoriasis', '0.03%', 'Immediate-release formulations of tacrolimus are indicated for the prophylaxis of organ rejection in adult and pediatric patients receiving allogeneic liver, kidney, heart, or lung transplants, in combination with other immunosuppressants.[L8162] Extended-release formulations of tacrolimus are indicated for the prophylaxis of organ rejection in adult and pediatric patients receiving kidney transplants, in combination with other immunosuppressants,[L20034,L41005] and may be used in patients converted from immediate-release formulations.[L41005]
